      <para id="id8880120">Now discuss in your groups the reasons for the specific design of each part of the outfit!</para>
      <para id="id12847170">b) <emphasis effect="bold">The legions could move about and attack in different formations. Explain, by means of sketches, how you would attack the following:</emphasis></para>
      <list id="id10278855" list-type="bulleted">
