      <para id="id12622354">c) <emphasis effect="bold">BRAINSTORM:</emphasis></para>
      <para id="id7842683">Explain to your friend why the Roman army became famous for its method of besieging a hostile city.</para>
      <figure id="id9225391">
        <media id="id9225391_media" alt="">
          <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics3-8468.png" id="id9225391__onlineimage" height="333" width="471"/>
        </media>
