      <para id="id12769315">d) <emphasis effect="bold">Choose your own soldiers!</emphasis></para>
      <para id="id6287520">The following game to recognize causes and results will test your ability to its limits.</para>
      <para id="id3889331">Emperor Claudius decides to attack a hostile British tribe, the Britons. Unfortunately he has little money available, because they are busy building ships for the Empire, and they also have to pay thousands of soldiers. The abacus shows how much money you can spend (represented by the five beads.)</para>
      <para id="id12975812">First study the secret information that is provided below very carefully and help the emperor to calculate a suitable combination. Colour in the row of beads of your choice. The cost is indicated on each item e.g. LL.</para>
      <figure id="id6594078">
        <media id="id6594078_media" alt="">
          <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics4-60bc.png" id="id6594078__onlineimage" height="437" width="536"/>
